OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKing hails Mandela         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffriendship on South Africa 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fvisit                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, King Charles has spoken of the strong  
OL,6, friendship between the late Queen      
OL,7, Elizabeth and Nelson Mandela, as the   
OL,8, King hosted a state visit by South     
OL,9, Africa's current president.            
OL,11,FAt a banquet in Buckingham Palace, the 
OL,12,FKing welcomed Cyril Ramaphosa and      
OL,13,Fhailed the cultural and trading links  
OL,14,Fbetween the UK and South Africa.       
OL,16,FBut the King also acknowledged the     
OL,17,Fdifficult legacy of colonialism.       
OL,19,FHe said there were "elements of that   
OL,20,Fhistory which provoke profound sorrow".
